Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice melody...\NAmazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less is to expect from a first-class world-famous \Npianist's performance. A bliss for the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as the concert is over, \Ncountless banquets await her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only the way her arms sway,\Nbut her whole style is top-notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... Don't you have a more important \Neditor-in-chief business?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a diversion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished... already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Piano concerts tend to captivate one \Nwithout even noticing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know? Turns out pressing the piano keys \Nrequires a remarkable strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, pianists fingers are dexterous \Nand hands are firm and steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But her fingers look so slim and feminine. \NYou'd never tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all the more surprising this pianist \Ncontacted us herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Namely, the Turning Gears magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She invited us to her concert,\Ntaking place on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, seems like we're to join a high society soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why pick such a peculiar venue for a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That I wonder myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care about the details? \NIf we are welcome, we are not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just accept her hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, Ginya, \Nyou're free this Sunday, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is there to hesitate about? Such a bonus from the editor is to be accepted without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonus, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our invitation allows for 5 people to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:22.21,Song,,0,0,10,,{\fade(700,700)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\blur1.5\3c&H384441&\4c&H4D4743&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\fscx114\fscy92}Episode 4 \N {\fs86}Melody
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, only the editor and Ishibashi decided to come, and then there's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With two more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Party on board a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, I'm taken along just to fill the gap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm also allowed to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! Mainly - because this time \NI'm taking you out not at my own expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, of course! \NI knew it all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding this Teresa, the pianist who invited you... \NShe is from Spain, ain't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you know her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her on TV on Channel 23.\NAnd her performance is damn fine. I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With such face, you're versed in classic piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look that philistine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Master should also come. We still have one more vacancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No no! I'm not much of a Hearty \Nnor a fan of banquets, so I better refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, if I yield and agree to come, \Nyou'll make fun of me again. Can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, \Nthe last spot remains vacant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who is this one more person you invited?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you don't know either? \NFar as I'm aware, it's some young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon we'll meet her and know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I am here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Did we make you wait? \NYour seat is there. In the back, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so... familiar. \NWhat kind of relationship they have? Any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But parties require dresses, \Nand I only have my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, fine. The invitation says no dress code is applied, \Nso nothing to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No more hesitation. \NHurry up and hop into my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cheeky as ever, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd never think Ginya has a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Mai. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are glad to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri and Ginya having a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, don't be so nervous, Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having anything but a date. Just attending a show \Nand a dinner party on the ship, nothing aside that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... A dinner party is a big deal, \Nespecially - with Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The one living on cheap bentos \Nfrom convenience stores!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, in her heart, Yuri never wanted \Nto accompany Ginya to such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, see.\NIt's Yuri's sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You get so carried away talking about Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were this aroused and erratic just yesterday. \NIt's great to be young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't comprehend it myself, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I desire to attend this dinner party myself. \NThough I'd be way more comfortable without Ginya there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the case. All the more clear \Nwhy she agreed to go so willingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! How did he dare to invite Yuri!? \NGinya is not even a human! Bloody animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Aren't those your precious children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! I wanna go there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, to everyone who managed to attend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa Sam N'Kota's special party, \Ncelebrating her visit to Japan, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Our honorable guests may proceed onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we differ in our suits only, \NI still feel completely out of place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! \NNever have I seen that kind of luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ishibashi, Yuri, \Nshall we try everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all on your brother's courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable how tangible his work gets sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not every time it results \Nin visiting such a splendid ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We parted some time ago, so I live with my step-uncle now. I wonder if he minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A step uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be calling him uncle, \Nbut he is like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Albeit we're not even blood related.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, brother chose to stay in the city \Nwhere he is comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it suits him. \NHence I have reasonable concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I'm relieved to see you tend to him \Nand I'm grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some, have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? You look bored.\NYou didn't happen to develop a seasick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand it one bit. \NWhat's the point inviting us to this kind of party?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a curious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They say excessive anxiety makes your sake taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is Teresa herself.\NTeresa Sam N'Kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She is so unbelievably beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see her pretty face has nothing to do \Nwith her recognition as genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She fixed a solo concert onboard a ship.\NIt must be absurd expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To say the least...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Restroom is taking him longer than planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa sure was kind, \Nand I never regretted attending this banquet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I'm even more convinced now - \Nsuch flawless play is a true art onboard a rocking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot machines on the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot machines on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, of all the places?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something I would like to know...\NAny ideas, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of ideas you expect me to utter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Turning Gears magazine, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope today's cuisine \Nmeets your tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa Sam N'Kota!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi Ginya, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One of your recent articles\Npiqued my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,While reading your article, \NI felt as if I was reading my own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you play pachislot yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder in which way these fingers \Npress the machine buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The pachislot rhythm is similar to the piano rhythm. \NDon't you think piano and pachislot are akin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked your fingers to make sure of my suggestion. \NWould you care to reciprocate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what pachislot rhythm is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you do me the honor if I challenge you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me state the rules specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Special identical pachislot machines \Nare installed on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them has a time limit.\NInstead, the victor should manage to hit the big first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we have a whole ship of spectators. \NWe're to be exhibited like in a gallery. Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. Let's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginya, is this really okay?\NShe is much more used to such conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,While you are just a novice pachislot journalist.\NNot even a real slotter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All you know is bare theory.\NIt's obviously insufficient for the victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lose, \Nthe whole Turning Gears magazine is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa is an unmatched pianist.\NBut an excellent slotter at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it the moment I touched her finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why however big the bets are, \NI can't turn down Teresa's challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover - she challenged the whole \NTurning Gears magazine today. So I must accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, on Miss Teresa's request, \Nwe begin the additional special program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The showdown will now take place \Nagainst the Turning Gears' representative, Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, for your convenience, \Nthe game is broadcasted on a large screen behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever hits the big first - wins...\NI need to get used to the drums speed faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rocking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... That's the point of the ship. \NAlthough docked, it still rocks on the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one hell of inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are participants ready to begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the battle began! Which one will hit the big first - \Nwill it be Teresa? Or else... will it be Otonashi Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Started with the Neo! \NKeep it this way, Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Editor, is brother winning this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That's still unclear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I only get Small Factors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa plays with her eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But how does she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she planning to rely on blind luck only?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa is already running a significant streak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you play with your eyes closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea it is possible. Editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She plays exactly the same way as with piano, \Nletting the body follow the rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her ears tell her about the machine's state \Nand when to press the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep calm, Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way! Ginya has almost hit Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His finger slipped off due to the ship rocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, pull yourself together! \NYou will win if you calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, I can't hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it's strong, sometimes it's weak.\NBut a constant rhythm is inherent even in the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use opposing the rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like... playing the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Success! Teresa's first Riichi is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She takes advantage of the wave pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi has also closed his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhythm, you say? \NI need to catch that rhythm and move with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Brother is winning!\NHe combined three titles before Teresa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait... He did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A Regular...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Miss Teresa's Big!\NThe game is concluded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm smashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Acknowledging one's defeat is important, \Nbut wasn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won today only thanks to this rocking ship as a handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This time the ship served me a home field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But next time I hope to face you on even grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time we leave.\NShall we go home, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so humiliating. \NI feel sorry for Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.\NHe's my brother after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ginya won't get upset \Nover one loss, however devastating it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unusual paper airplane you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not folded any since childhood, \Nso I may have messed it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it flies well enough, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think you lost \Nonly because the waves were rocking the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa allowed her keen senses to drive her.\NShe followed her own rhythm all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, your conviction of only one legit way to victory led you to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Led me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what differentiates the winner from the loser today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All experienced slotters come up with their own \Nstyle of play, which they stick to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot about how to play pachislot right. \NBut that knowledge stands in your way to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, I even believed \Nthat you could actually win.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As a writer, you should not run from this defeat \Nfor the sake of good articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the only way your articles remain sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, won't it be nice for Turning Gears \Nto have a man to stand up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. One hell of unfortunate.\NBut more than that, I experience some kind of refreshment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Refreshed after being beaten?\NThat taste of yours is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, don't you think you grew through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocking me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean any mockery!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it's the effect of today's hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I may share it with you someday.\NYou'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing else to surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya! We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming! \NMai, let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, brother!\NBrother, you cheat!
