Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Slotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \NFuture.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will \Nstop the time.
